text: The Panama national under-20 football team represents Panama in youth international football. They have qualified for the FIFA U-20 World Cup six times where their best placing was at the Round of 16 at the 2019 FIFA U-20 World Cup in Poland. ==Honours== Major competitions * CONCACAF Under-20 Championship ** Runners-up (1): 2015 ==References== Category:National under-20 football teams Category:National sports teams of Panama Category:Football in Panama
